{"tid":488004,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手後做朋友係唔係好傻？","createTime":"2017-12-03T09:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T00:05:02.000Z","uid":54685,"like":30,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f4dc6f97acb84c69ae431c0debaa990ac37b6088","tid":488004,"uid":54685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T09:51:10.000Z","msg":"一齊四年啱啱分手<br />\n過去呢年都係longd<br />\n我一半嘅人生都有佢嘅存在<br />\n因為小學就識<br />\n一開始以為大家都可以<br />\n最後開口講分手嘅竟然係佢<br />\n好多原因，唔成熟無話題<br />\n佢需要我個陣唔係身邊，好多野我幫唔到佢<br />\n加上longd辛苦，維持落去大家難受<br />\n<br />\n我以為我地有得救，特登飛去搵佢<br />\n最後都係無得救<br />\n宜家自己一個係英國<br />\n仲諗緊可唔可以做返朋友<br />\n因為我地中間無第三者<br />\n而且我覺得佢仲中意我<br />\n只係longd令人感覺磨滅<br />\n就算今次一齊返，最後無得見都係還原基本步<br />\n問左兩次點樣先可以令佢對我有返感覺<br />\n佢答我唔係呢個時候<br />\n到宜家我都仲諗會唔會兩三年後<br />\n唔洗longd，大家又成熟左，可以一齊返<br />\n好想話佢知呢段時間我可以等<br />\n唔係話傻傻地等，係呢段時間大家做自己嘅野<br />\n我地冷靜返後，做返朋友<br />\n然後有日可以再一齊返<br />\n其實我咁做，係咪好傻？<br />\n<br />\n我知你有時上連登，我怕你會知道我咁諗不過如果你睇到嘅，好想同你講<br />\n希望我地嘅未來會有對方嘅存在<br />\n當我地再大個，可以成為大家嘅唯一<br />\n呢個係我宜家生存嘅動力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">第一次見到你咁決絕，真係好hurt，你嘅好同壞我全部都中意，我愛你</span>"},{"pid":"0b57b0ed994d40d04793a015b74829cd344dae38","tid":488004,"uid":54685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:00:08.000Z","msg":"有無人吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48caf8acce915a7f0354d972633b4e39f467bcd5","tid":488004,"uid":16594,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:01:57.000Z","msg":"點會做得返朋友(短期內...)<br />\n搭下火車去下其他地方玩 世界好大 唔好錯過沿途風景"},{"pid":"84980335ea3f8f004cbdb35d3a457dff10f26f19","tid":488004,"uid":115339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:02:11.000Z","msg":"痴心肉便器"},{"pid":"93e13767676d6c25ec6a272e4d55285601e6b4fd","tid":488004,"uid":42510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:02:32.000Z","msg":"巴打，我都係自己一個係英國讀書，telegram 陪你傾？"},{"pid":"1dcc8973821018298440f2323e3446d7d59acba4","tid":488004,"uid":66119,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:05:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">因為我地中間無第三者</span><br />\n<br />\n等多一兩個月先講"},{"pid":"0413ebee64c2ac5244ebee2ee575dc6db242eefb","tid":488004,"uid":54685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:20:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">因為我地中間無第三者</span><br />\n<br />\n等多一兩個月先講</blockquote><br />\n唔好hurt我啦，不想面對現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5561bd6bdf84769e0e537f1fe82b9f5063184741","tid":488004,"uid":54685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:21:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點會做得返朋友(短期內...)<br />\n搭下火車去下其他地方玩 世界好大 唔好錯過沿途風景</blockquote><br />\n梗係唔係短期內<br />\n只係希望有日可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04686dc842d3874804e912b8a53cb331208716a6","tid":488004,"uid":54685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:21:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打，我都係自己一個係英國讀書，telegram 陪你傾？</blockquote><br />\n巴打英國邊到"},{"pid":"042839cf46e4d7b92168fb181c51015ef3cb8ca5","tid":488004,"uid":54685,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:23:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴心肉便器</blockquote><br />\n當佢遇多幾個女仔之後一定後悔今日飛左我<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望佢咁諗</span></span>"},{"pid":"16e56fe75f1261caa3e01c4e460cd4b21c991e1c","tid":488004,"uid":54685,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T11:06:07.000Z","msg":"好想聽到複合成功例子安慰自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0320be05c3b3ce089eed50270b65d96b2657f35","tid":488004,"uid":59795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T11:09:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而且我覺得佢仲中意我</blockquote><br />\n你諗姐 唔肯面對現實 正辣殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a54eb1c9ba569f67f5a6c5920b8df4da1d9d98e","tid":488004,"uid":89595,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T11:14:45.000Z","msg":"同你既情況一模一樣 我自己算係呃緊自己放低左佢 但係好似都係喺度癡心妄想咁等待未來我地兩個會從新再相遇 命運會再交叉.... 好想聽到有成功例子 究竟離離合合既感情有無可能...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebaf3f495bfd3fb2f7e67541afb1601488809d76","tid":488004,"uid":142577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T11:16:20.000Z","msg":"long d真係好易淡<br />\n一嘈交就冇彎轉<br />\n冇feel都做唔到乜嘢去補救<br />\n望住佢消失又乜野都做唔到嗰種感覺好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53faca42a3ea709fbde6535f90c0405ee060fd20","tid":488004,"uid":54685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T12:32:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你既情況一模一樣 我自己算係呃緊自己放低左佢 但係好似都係喺度癡心妄想咁等待未來我地兩個會從新再相遇 命運會再交叉.... 好想聽到有成功例子 究竟離離合合既感情有無可能...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個心好似有個窿咁 <br />\n我都好想知有無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe858d8807c5ddac06b2f6af1aacdff402e1e21","tid":488004,"uid":54685,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T12:39:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>long d真係好易淡<br />\n一嘈交就冇彎轉<br />\n冇feel都做唔到乜嘢去補救<br />\n望住佢消失又乜野都做唔到嗰種感覺好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打，見到你個名<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為咁我先飛過去 <br />\n就係因為係香港咩都做唔到嘅無力感好辛苦<br />\n唔想坐係香港被人飛等死<br />\n希望可以有一絲絲嘅機會都唔好放過去挽留<br />\n已經係叫分手跟住即晚買機票第二日就飛<br />\n仲有考試essay未寫都放低曬<br />\n身邊啲朋友都睇唔過眼覺得好痴線<br />\n去到仲要俾佢話點解咁衝動我過去有咩用<br />\n我只係想努力爭取<br />\n唔想第日後悔無盡全力去挽留<br />\n宜家搵朋友周圍去玩<br />\n算係將自己感情係個到做終結翻香港要重新嚟過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好希望佢會覺得飛左我係錯嘅決定<br />\n然後搵返我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6ae8f6d944ee3b7072168d5d0728425f212dfe","tid":488004,"uid":33004,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T12:45:39.000Z","msg":"Long d 100%散<br />\n兩個年輕人 拍拖梗係想對方係身邊<br />\n唔係身邊既 拍黎把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n神交好過喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係冬天 個人一凍又無伴侶 凍上加凍"},{"pid":"d217911bfb961bd5a7b90d1462568aa77bc70378","tid":488004,"uid":26008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T12:51:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係</span>"},{"pid":"8c035ce717a474fc61db3ba90e21d2d61cee2a16","tid":488004,"uid":142017,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T12:56:57.000Z","msg":"兩三年既時間 好多野可以變 唔係唔可以等 不過好似俾緊假希望自己 怕你希望愈大失望愈大 同埋佢或者你會唔會識到新歡都係問題之一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過見到你一分手即買機票飛過去 唔知應該欣賞你痴心一片定係覺得你太傻 btw希望樓主可以同朋友出去散下心 唔洗自己一個唔開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e62a6204ba857201bf328b263ac12a30409bee5","tid":488004,"uid":46935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T13:52:02.000Z","msg":"分完keep住做左成年朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼續做朋友最後辛苦既係自己,所以已經決定唔再聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67298252a239242bc7b1a12d6e2df7d7ea632a27","tid":488004,"uid":54685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T14:15:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩三年既時間 好多野可以變 唔係唔可以等 不過好似俾緊假希望自己 怕你希望愈大失望愈大 同埋佢或者你會唔會識到新歡都係問題之一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過見到你一分手即買機票飛過去 唔知應該欣賞你痴心一片定係覺得你太傻 btw希望樓主可以同朋友出去散下心 唔洗自己一個唔開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n假希望好似先係我宜家生存嘅動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好傻吖我真係 宜家去搵下fd玩散心"},{"pid":"4c923bcef6899a98c51b473147ba1479787ddb1b","tid":488004,"uid":54685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T14:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分完keep住做左成年朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼續做朋友最後辛苦既係自己,所以已經決定唔再聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係分左仲keep住whatsapp搵大家出街咁？<br />\n唔係分耐啲先咁做會好啲？<br />\n不過有個朋友又係咁 斷斷續續六年"},{"pid":"1f3bae49803fdeaa01a589ef77f56ca5fbe0b47a","tid":488004,"uid":47005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T14:20:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兩三年既時間 好多野可以變 唔係唔可以等 不過好似俾緊假希望自己 怕你希望愈大失望愈大 同埋佢或者你會唔會識到新歡都係問題之一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過見到你一分手即買機票飛過去 唔知應該欣賞你痴心一片定係覺得你太傻 btw希望樓主可以同朋友出去散下心 唔洗自己一個唔開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n假希望好似先係我宜家生存嘅動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好傻吖我真係 宜家去搵下fd玩散心</blockquote><br />\n咁你咪當住仲有希望, 四圍行下睇下風景識唔同人。"},{"pid":"a98221597956ee67c5a1336b8cd85e11f8f3c9d5","tid":488004,"uid":46935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T14:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>分完keep住做左成年朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼續做朋友最後辛苦既係自己,所以已經決定唔再聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係分左仲keep住whatsapp搵大家出街咁？<br />\n唔係分耐啲先咁做會好啲？<br />\n不過有